metadata.name: Universal Traveler #1
metadata.description:
Universal Travelers - or gods, as you may know them - are a genesis collection of 100 powerful beings scattered throughout time and space that have come to shape the universe as we currently know it. 

A true 1/1 collection emphasizing community engagement, owning a Universal Traveler grants holders the power to influence the story of their traveler - and the project as a whole.
